Kind: captions
Language: en

00:00:01.350 --> 00:00:02.029
PRESENTER: Hi, everybody.

00:00:02.029 --> 00:00:03.500
And thank you for joining
us today.

00:00:03.500 --> 00:00:05.660
We've got a great Google Talk
coming up and I have the

00:00:05.660 --> 00:00:08.830
pleasure of introducing our
speaker, Paddy Hirsch.

00:00:08.830 --> 00:00:11.660
