00:43:25.400 --> 00:43:28.930
You have these unscrupulous
investment companies that will

00:43:28.930 --> 00:43:32.230
go to old ladies and retired
people, and they'll say, oh,

00:43:32.230 --> 00:43:33.050
you should really buy this.

00:43:33.050 --> 00:43:34.660
It's going to return
you 9% a year.

00:43:34.660 --> 00:43:35.510
Everything's going to be fine.

00:43:35.510 --> 00:43:36.940
And then the next thing,
it disappears in the

00:43:36.940 --> 00:43:38.120
twinkle of an eye.

00:43:38.120 --> 00:43:38.780
That's illegal.

00:43:38.780 --> 00:43:40.360
And people go to
jail for that.

00:43:40.360 --> 00:43:41.710
What we have in the
investment banking

00:43:41.710 --> 00:43:44.030
system is that you have--

00:43:44.030 --> 00:43:47.080
say, one investment bank will go
to another investment bank

00:43:47.080 --> 00:43:49.900
and say, you should
buy this product.

00:43:49.900 --> 00:43:51.340
This product is complete
rubbish.

00:43:51.340 --> 00:43:53.660
Put lipstick on that pig.

00:43:53.660 --> 00:43:55.030
They know that it's
a bad product.

00:43:55.030 --> 00:43:55.660
And what are they doing?

00:43:55.660 --> 00:43:58.000
Not only are they selling it to
that-- or they believe it's

00:43:58.000 --> 00:43:58.560
a bad product.

00:43:58.560 --> 00:44:00.490
They're not only selling it to
that person, to that other

00:44:00.490 --> 00:44:03.050
investment bank, but they're
also betting against it.

00:44:03.050 --> 00:44:05.360
They're saying, we think it's
so bad, we're actually going

00:44:05.360 --> 00:44:08.010
to bet against this thing.

00:44:08.010 --> 00:44:10.000
There's a concept in investment
banking called "big

00:44:10.000 --> 00:44:14.380
boy language." It
goes into all of

00:44:14.380 --> 00:44:15.470
these investing documents.

00:44:15.470 --> 00:44:18.140
So you get a bank loan-- if
you buy a piece of a bank

00:44:18.140 --> 00:44:20.320
loan, they put this thing in
called big boy language, and

00:44:20.320 --> 00:44:22.910
basically it's saying, you
and I are big boys.

00:44:22.910 --> 00:44:24.530
We know what's going on here.

00:44:24.530 --> 00:44:26.760
This thing could be complete
rubbish, but you're buying it

00:44:26.760 --> 00:44:28.960
on site and you know it could
be complete rubbish.

00:44:28.960 --> 00:44:30.780
But you're going to
buy it anyway.

00:44:30.780 --> 00:44:34.020
And once you've signed the big
boy language, there's nothing

00:44:34.020 --> 00:44:34.560
you can do.

00:44:34.560 --> 00:44:37.640
The investment bank who bought
it, and it went right into the

00:44:37.640 --> 00:44:40.190
toilet 10 seconds later,
can scream and howl

00:44:40.190 --> 00:44:41.490
as much as it wants.

00:44:41.490 --> 00:44:43.370
The other bank will just flick
this big boy language and say,

00:44:43.370 --> 00:44:44.460
look, here it is.

00:44:44.460 --> 00:44:45.750
You signed a paper.

00:44:45.750 --> 00:44:51.310
So the other point is that it's
kind of like gambling.

00:44:51.310 --> 00:44:54.400
If you make a bet on something,
somebody's got to

00:44:54.400 --> 00:44:55.630
take the other side
of the action.

00:44:55.630 --> 00:44:58.400
You go to a bookie and you make
a bet on a horse, the

00:44:58.400 --> 00:45:00.500
bookie's taking the other
side of that action.

00:45:00.500 --> 00:45:04.680
The same goes with
investment banks.

00:45:04.680 --> 00:45:05.910
They're making bets on things.

00:45:05.910 --> 00:45:07.540
And somebody else has to
take the other side.

00:45:07.540 --> 00:45:10.220
Somebody's got to sell you
something in order

00:45:10.220 --> 00:45:11.420
for you to buy it.

00:45:11.420 --> 00:45:13.250
So all they're saying
is, listen, we're

00:45:13.250 --> 00:45:14.440
selling you this thing.

00:45:14.440 --> 00:45:16.040
We may bet against it.

00:45:16.040 --> 00:45:17.440
Here's the big boy language.

00:45:17.440 --> 00:45:19.430
But they're like, OK,
we'll take it.

00:45:19.430 --> 00:45:22.190
We think it's going to do
better than you do.

00:45:22.190 --> 00:45:24.120
And we'll take our chances.

00:45:24.120 --> 00:45:27.780
So yes, on the face of it to
us, it sounds incredible.

00:45:27.780 --> 00:45:29.360
It sounds illegal.

00:45:29.360 --> 00:45:32.050
But in fact it's absolutely
legal and it's been happening

00:45:32.050 --> 00:45:33.300
for decades.

